What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Pet Food Ingredients Market?

Market Analysis and Size

Pet food ingredients market find application in formulating balanced and nutritious diets for companion animals, including dogs, cats, and others. These ingredients, such as proteins, grains, vitamins, and minerals, contribute to the overall health, energy levels, and well-being of pets, meeting their dietary requirements and preferences.

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the global pet food ingredients market, which was USD 34.56 billion in 2023, is expected to reach USD 54.66 billion by 2031, at a CAGR of 5.9% during the forecast period 2024 to 2031. In addition to the insights on market scenarios such as market value, growth rate, segmentation, geographical coverage, and major players, the market reports curated by the Data Bridge Market Research also include depth expert analysis, patient epidemiology, pipeline analysis, pricing analysis, and regulatory framework.

